Package: PowStat
Title: Clinical Trial Sample Size Calculation and Statistical Design
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("PowStat", "Chen Chao", , "chenchaostat@163.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A client-server R package for clinical trial sample size 
    calculation and statistical design. Supports continuous, binary, and 
    time-to-event endpoints with fixed and group sequential designs. 
    Core computations run on a server; 
    the client package provides a lightweight API interface.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://github.com/chenchaostat/PowStat
BugReports: https://github.com/chenchaostat/PowStat/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Depends:
    rlang
Imports:
    httr2 (>= 1.0.0),
    cli (>= 3.0.0)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    rmarkdown,
    ggplot2,
    jsonlite
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
